---
Source:
  Title: A Year with Hafiz
  Translator: Daniel Ladinsky
  Author: Hafiz
  ISBN: 978-0143117544
  Publisher: Penguin Books
Format: Verse
By: Hafiz
Title: Nothing Can Shatter This Love
Description: December 2
---
Nothing can shatter this love.
For even if you took another

into your arms, the truth is,
my sweetheart, you would

still

be

kissing

me.
